subject: KYC Status Update — {{ kyc_status }}
<h2>KYC Document Status</h2>
<p>Dear {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your KYC document status has been updated to: <strong>{{ kyc_status }}</strong></p>
{% if kyc_status == "Verified" %}
<p>You are now verified and can proceed to rent bikes at any of our hubs.</p>
{% elif kyc_status == "Rejected" %}
<p>Please upload new documents for review. Contact the hub for details on what went wrong.</p>
{% elif kyc_status == "Pending Review" %}
<p>Your documents are being reviewed. We will notify you once the verification is complete.</p>
{% else %}
<p>Please check your account for details.</p>
{% endif %}
